com.apusplay.sdk.pay

类 IabResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.apusplay.sdk.CallBackResult
      • com.apusplay.sdk.RequestResult
        • com.apusplay.sdk.pay.IabResult

  • public class IabResult
extends RequestResult
    Represents the result of an in-app billing operation. A result is composed of a response code (an integer) and possibly a message (String). You can get those by calling getResponse() and getMessage(), respectively. You can also inquire whether a result is a success or a failure by calling CallBackResult.isSuccess() and CallBackResult.isFailure().
